ITuy api-gateway

Environment required (.env)
- ENV                       eg. production|dev
- SERVER_PORT               eg. 3000
- FRONTEND_URL              eg. "*"  // cors
- PUBLIC_URL                eg. https://ituy-api.com/page
- SESSION_SECRET            eg. "ANY"
- JWT_SECRET                any value
- JWT_EXPIRES_IN            eg. 10d  // token expires 10 day
- YEARS_HISTORICAL_DATA     eg. 6  // 6 year 
# For email
- MAIL_USERNAME=your_email
- MAIL_PASSWORD=your_password


// Data from database after query if u need data
